snippet.title: One Lonely Outpost - Official Early Access Trailer | E3 2021
snippet.description:
Watch the latest trailer and get another look at One Lonely Outpost, coming to Early Access 2022.

Start a farming colony and grow it into a vibrant community. Choose from traditional animals and natural produce or opt for robo-cows and gene-spliced crops. You can take a break from farming by mining, socializing with colonists, finding a love interest, exploring alien ruins, and much more.

#GameTrailers #Gaming #E32021
